				<li><a href="http://www.13moon.com/time-is-art.htm">http://www.13moon.com</a> - Time is art</li>	
		        <li><a href="http://www.photon.net/13moon.php">Photon.Net 13 Moon Tool</a> - an awesome Galactic Overlay</li>
